<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff3_images/ff3_part_1-3/08-tokkul-006.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 右邊隔間的人會告訴你壁爐那裡有隱藏的樓梯 ( 其實好像不算是隱藏的XDDD )</p>
<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff3_images/ff3_part_1-3/08-tokkul-007.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 就從壁爐的入口進去</p>
<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff3_images/ff3_part_1-3/08-tokkul-008.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 兩個寶箱：<span style='color: #800000;'>雷蛇劍、功夫裝</span></p>
<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff3_images/ff3_part_1-3/08-tokkul-009.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 左邊的罈子裡 ( 拉近看 ) 還有一個「<span style='color: #800000;'>音速拳套</span>」</p>
