<p>這邊可以先繞到旅館的右後方，然後往上走</p>
<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff3_images/ff3_missed_items/07-ancients_village_new_item-002.png' width='486' height='326' /></p>
<p><span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span></p>
<p><span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span></p>
